            <div type="translation">
                <p>Aristocles(?) made (this).</p></div>
            
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The monument preserves the bare feet of a hoplite; the artwork and letter form is characteristic of late 6 c. Attica. The name of the sculptor Aristocles appears in similar monuments found in proximity, and he was plausibly created this item as well. </p></div>
            
            
